TITLE:: FbC
summary::  a painless way to create a feedback loop within a SynthDef.
categories:: UGens>Feedback
related:: Classes/Feedback, Classes/FbNode, Classes/Fb, Classes/FbL,  Classes/FbK







DESCRIPTION::



FbC is a cubically interpolating version of Fb, which is a convenience class that allows you to create feedback loops within a SynthDef in as painless a way as possible.



See link::Classes/Fb:: for discussion, usage and examples.
